story.text: The previous best weekend of my life was sailing in the British Virgin Islands last winter, maybe.

I got to see Caroline Goulding play under Domo and then a transformational concert in the Music Barn. That was topped off with incredible horseback riding and conversation on Sunday. Today I am reeling from sickness that has not abated - but certainly not strep throat (yay).
Elissa and Jimmy are here, and they are awesome!!!!
